00:23:23,620 --> 00:23:25,910
I will obey Your Majesty's decision.

256
00:23:37,110 --> 00:23:41,960
I know that it's difficult for you.

257
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:44,700
But if I don't say it now,

258
00:23:45,710 --> 00:23:48,610
